Package: rosario
Title: An Algorithm to Analyze Cyclical Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ángel L.", "Robles-Fernández", , "maria.h.m_1995@tamu.edu", role = c("aut"))
    person("Maria A.", "Hurtado-Materon", , "maria.h.m_1995@tamu.edu", role = c("aut"))
    person("Tatiana", "Velásquez-Roa", , "maria.h.m_1995@tamu.edu", role = c("aut"))
    person("Iván", "Castro-Arellano", , "maria.h.m_1995@tamu.edu", role = c("ths", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools to quantify and visualize temporal niche overlap
    among biological identities (species, populations, or other units) using
    indices (Pianka, Czekanowski) and null models. The package implements the
    ROSARIO algorithm (Castro-Arellano et al. 2010).
